CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. It designates the percentage rate of withholding on the specific type of income on the W-8BEN (Certificate of Foreign Status of Beneficial Owner for United States Tax Withholding).
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The percentage rate of withholding on the specific type of income on the W-8BEN (Certificate of Foreign Status of Beneficial Owner for United States Tax Withholding).
